            <p class="proj-desc">Full-stack system aligning Polar H10 ECG with BCG (PVDF Sensor). R peaks detected via SciPy's signal module; BCG J peaks extracted and filtered using z-score based thresholding to retain only high-confidence peaks. Cross-correlation between R and J peaks computes per-beat alignment. R-to-J peak matching with ±50ms delay handling and drift logging.</p>
